{"LanguageCode":"en","SurahData":{"Chapter":93,"Index":"093","Name":"Ad-Duhaa","TranslatedName":"The Morning Hours","ArabicName":"سُوْرَةُ الضُّحٰي","Revelation":"Mecca","RevelationOrder":11,"HasBismillah":true,"VerseCount":11,"SajdaCount":0,"JuzStart":30,"JuzEnd":30,"VerseStart":6080,"VerseEnd":6090,"ManzilStart":7,"ManzilEnd":7,"RukuStart":535,"RukuEnd":535,"MaqraStart":238,"MaqraEnd":238,"PageStart":596,"PageEnd":596},"Summaries":["<p>11 verses in 1 section. This Surah gives the message of hope and consolation. It reminds about Allah's blessings and the way the Believers should take these blessings.</p>"],"Verses":[{"Verse":1,"Text":"وَٱلضُّحَىٰ","End":"١"},{"Verse":2,"Text":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا سَجَىٰ","End":"٢"},{"Verse":3,"Text":"مَا وَدَّعَكَ رَبُّكَ وَمَا قَلَىٰ","End":"٣"},{"Verse":4,"Text":"وَلَلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ لَّكَ مِنَ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","End":"٤"},{"Verse":5,"Text":"وَلَسَوۡفَ يُعۡطِيكَ رَبُّكَ فَتَرۡضَىٰٓ","End":"٥"},{"Verse":6,"Text":"أَلَمۡ يَجِدۡكَ يَتِيمٗا فَـَٔاوَىٰ","End":"٦"},{"Verse":7,"Text":"وَوَجَدَكَ ضَآلّٗا فَهَدَىٰ","End":"٧"},{"Verse":8,"Text":"وَوَجَدَكَ عَآئِلٗا فَأَغۡنَىٰ","End":"٨"},{"Verse":9,"Text":"فَأَمَّا ٱلۡيَتِيمَ فَلَا تَقۡهَرۡ","End":"٩"},{"Verse":10,"Text":"وَأَمَّا ٱلسَّآئِلَ فَلَا تَنۡهَرۡ","End":"١٠"},{"Verse":11,"Text":"وَأَمَّا بِنِعۡمَةِ رَبِّكَ فَحَدِّثۡ","End":"١١"}],"Translations":[{"LanguageCode":"eng","Language":"English","Name":"eng-mustafakhattabg","Author":"Mustafa Khattab God Edition","Source":"","Direction":"ltr","Translations":[{"Verse":1,"Text":"By the morning sunlight"},{"Verse":2,"Text":"and the night when it falls still"},{"Verse":3,"Text":"Your Lord ˹O Prophet˺ has not abandoned you, nor has He become hateful ˹of you˺"},{"Verse":4,"Text":"And the next life is certainly far better for you than this one"},{"Verse":5,"Text":"And ˹surely˺ your Lord will give so much to you that you will be pleased"},{"Verse":6,"Text":"Did He not find you as an orphan then sheltered you"},{"Verse":7,"Text":"Did He not find you unguided then guided you"},{"Verse":8,"Text":"And did He not find you needy then satisfied your needs"},{"Verse":9,"Text":"So do not oppress the orphan"},{"Verse":10,"Text":"nor repulse the beggar"},{"Verse":11,"Text":"And proclaim the blessings of your Lord"}]}]}